content:
Reduce long transfer destination lists when agents just need to deliver a session to the right place quickly. Choose whether to offer all queues, flows, and profiles, or just offer some.

Where: This change is available to all enhanced Messaging channels and Messaging for In-App and Web.

How: Go to Presence Configurations in Setup and edit the transfer destinations. Then save your changes.

Customize Which Queues, Flows, and Profiles Your Agents Can Transfer To
title: Customize Agent Transfer Destinations in Messaging
